high_descs: Turn left and face the counter by the stove in front of you.
Take a potato from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink to your right.
Place the potato in the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the white table in front of you.
Take another potato from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the potato in the sink in front of you.
Turn completely around, move slightly forward, turn right and walk to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the potato lying on the counter.
Turn completely around, walk to the refrigerator, turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the potato in the smaller left side of the sink.
Turn right, move slightly forward, turn right and walk to the table.
Pick up the potato sitting on the front of the table next to the green sponge.
Turn right, walk to the refrigerator, turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the potato in the larger right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put both potatoes in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk towards the kitchen counter.
Pick up the potato on the left of the spatula.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the right of the toaster.
Put the potato in the sink on the left.
Turn around and go to the table with the lettuce on it.
Pick up the potato that is on the left of the egg.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Put the potato into the larger sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put potatoes into the two sinks.
